      <title>美国创纪录高位提振市场情绪，亚洲股市攀升：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国通胀数据公布之前美国股市创下新高，亚洲股市周四上涨，这可能有助于影响美联储未来几个月的政策放松。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 22:24:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>B. Riley 贷款机构每周获得修订后的贷款流动性更新</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/b-riley-lenders-get-weekly-liquidity-updates-in-revised-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[B. Riley Financial Inc. 的贷方正在对公司的财务状况进行更多的监督，包括每周更新其流动性和一些交易情况，以努力使这家亏损的投资公司摆脱困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/b-riley-lenders-get-weekly-liquidity-updates-in-revised-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 19:28:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伯克希尔发行 2820 亿日元债券，激发日本投资希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/berkshire-yen-bond-sale-fuels-talk-of-fresh-japan-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃伦·巴菲特旗下的伯克希尔哈撒韦公司周四出售了价值 2818 亿日元（18.9 亿美元）的多档债券，此举引发了人们对这位传奇投资者将增加对日本资产的投资的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/berkshire-yen-bond-sale-fuels-talk-of-fresh-japan-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 10:13:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
